Please follow the instructions given in the following link to setup nginx server with uwsgi interface :

For ubuntu 16.04 :

https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-serve-flask-applications-with-uwsgi-and-nginx-on-ubuntu-16-04

For ubuntu 14.04 :

https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-serve-flask-applications-with-uwsgi-and-nginx-on-ubuntu-14-04


Project Structure :

dashboard--->
		static-->
			css
			js
			images
		
		templates-->
			mobile
			desktop
		
		application.py

				



To set the path for static folder ,go to application.py and change the 'static_path' variable value.

